properties.Name: CollectionTelephoneCall
properties.Description:
A collection contact made via a telephone call,

Telephone calls are an efficient way to contact a large number of parties and much less costly that personal visits.

Columns.Name: CollectionEventId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a collection event.

Columns.Name: ConversationNote
Columns.Description: Notes, comment or additional details regarding the collection telephone call.

Columns.Name: OutstandingAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of debt outstanding at the time of the collection telephone call.

Columns.Name: CollectedAmount
Columns.Description: The amount collected or pledged during the collection telephone call.

Columns.Name: PlannedFollowupCollectionActivityDate
Columns.Description: The date of the planned followup activity to the collection telephone call.

Columns.Name: CollectionTelephoneCallTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Collection Telephone Call Type.

Columns.Name: FollowupCollectionActivityId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Followup Collection Activity Type.
